#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn22.18"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.18:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.18:0.2"
msgid "2. Aniccavagga "
msgstr "2. Impermanence "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 18. Sahetuaniccasutta → paṭhamahetusuttaṃ (bj) | hetu 1 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn22.18:0.3"
msgid "18. Sahetuaniccasutta "
msgstr "18. Impermanence With Its Cause "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn22.18:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.18:1.2"
msgid "“Rūpaṃ, bhikkhave, aniccaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, form is impermanent. "

msgctxt "sn22.18:1.3"
msgid "Yopi hetu, yopi paccayo rūpassa uppādāya, sopi anicco. "
msgstr "The cause and condition that gives rise to form is also impermanent. "

msgctxt "sn22.18:1.4"
msgid "Aniccasambhūtaṃ, bhikkhave, rūpaṃ kuto niccaṃ bhavissati. "
msgstr "Since form is produced by what is impermanent, how could it be permanent? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.18:1.5"
msgid "Vedanā aniccā. "
msgstr "Feeling is impermanent … "

msgctxt "sn22.18:1.6"
msgid "Yopi hetu, yopi paccayo vedanāya uppādāya, sopi anicco. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn22.18:1.7"
msgid "Aniccasambhūtā, bhikkhave, vedanā kuto niccā bhavissati. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.18:1.8"
msgid "Saññā aniccā … "
msgstr "Perception is impermanent … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.18:1.9"
msgid "saṅkhārā aniccā. "
msgstr "Choices are impermanent … "

msgctxt "sn22.18:1.10"
msgid "Yopi hetu yopi paccayo saṅkhārānaṃ uppādāya, sopi anicco. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn22.18:1.11"
msgid "Aniccasambhūtā, bhikkhave, saṅkhārā kuto niccā bhavissanti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.18:1.12"
msgid "Viññāṇaṃ aniccaṃ. "
msgstr "Consciousness is impermanent. "

msgctxt "sn22.18:1.13"
msgid "Yopi hetu yopi paccayo viññāṇassa uppādāya, sopi anicco. "
msgstr "The cause and condition that gives rise to consciousness is also impermanent. "

msgctxt "sn22.18:1.14"
msgid "Aniccasambhūtaṃ, bhikkhave, viññāṇaṃ kuto niccaṃ bhavissati. "
msgstr "Since consciousness is produced by what is impermanent, how could it be permanent? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.18:1.15"
msgid "Evaṃ passaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "Seeing this … "

msgctxt "sn22.18:1.16"
msgid "nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti pajānātī”ti. "
msgstr "They understand: ‘… there is no return to any state of existence.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.18:1.17"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

